SUMMARY:Paws and Purrs Adoption Saturday
DESCRIPTION:Join us during our extended weekend hours for this special monthly event\, Paws and Purrs Adoption Saturday! Our furry friends are here and ready to meet you! \nOur center is located at 6003 Chapel Hill Road\, Suite 133 in Raleigh\, NC 27607. We’ll be open for this event from 12pm to 3pm\, and we hope you’ll join us.
URL:https://secondchancenc.org/event/paws-and-purrs-adoption-saturday-7/
LOCATION:Second Chance Pet Adoptions\, 6003 Chapel Hill Road\, Suite 133\, Raleigh\, NC\, 27519\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://secondchancenc.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Internal_Events_FeaturedImage_PPAD.png
END:VEVENT
