SUMMARY:Spring Fling with Unleashed
DESCRIPTION:Join us for another wonderful afternoon at the Spring Fling with Unleashed! We’ll have some of our adorable adoptables there to visit with as well as raffle prizes\, info about the Second Chance mission\, and more! There will be a Doggie Easter Egg Hunt\, vendors\, animal fundraisers\, food trucks\, drinks\, and more to enjoy from Unleashed\, too. \n📍 Koka Booth Amphitheatre at 8003 Regency Pkwy\, Cary\, NC 27518 \n📅 Sunday\, April 26\, 2026 from 12-6 p.m.
URL:https://secondchancenc.org/event/spring-fling-with-unleashed/
LOCATION:Koka Booth Amphitheatre\, 8003 Regency Parkway\, Cary\, NC\, 27518
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secondchancenc.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/SF-2026-Graphic-e1769545446173.jpg
END:VEVENT
